<h1 id="3">Map Applicating</h1>
<h2 id="3-1">Requirements</h2>
<ul>
	<li>A desktop with Among Us installed</li>
	Where you downloaded Among Us from does not matter. LevelImposter is tested with Steam, Epic, and Itch.io.
	<li>BepInEx applied to Among Us</li>
	If you have modded Among Us in the past, you likely already have BepInEx installed. See
	<a href="https://docs.reactor.gg/docs/basic/install_bepinex">Reactor's guide</a> on how to install BepInEx in Among Us.
	<i>(Note: LevelImposter does <b>not</b> require Reactor to be installed)</i>
</ul>
<h2 id="3-2">Automatic Method</h2>
<ol>
	<li>Close Among Us</li>
	<li>Download the latest LevelImposter Client on <a href="https://github.com/DigiWorm0/LevelImposter/releases">GitHub</a></li>
	<li>Run LevelImposter.exe</li>
	<li>Hit "Browse" and select your map JSON</li>
	<li>Hit "Apply"</li>
	<li>Open Among Us</li>
</ol>
<p>
	If LevelImposter succeeded, it should run without issue. If not, feel free to contact us at our discord server: <a href="https://discord.gg/9jJEBQ4qJs">https://discord.gg/9jJEBQ4qJs</a>
</p>

<h2 id="3-3">Manual Method</h2>
<p>
	If you are having trouble running the automatic installer, you can try manually installing LevelImposter.
</p>
<ol>
	<li>Close Among Us</li>
	<li>Go to LevelImposter > LevelImposter-Installer > Resources at our github page or click <a href="https://github.com/DigiWorm0/LevelImposter/tree/master/LevelImposter-Installer/Resources">here</a>.</li>
	<li>Download both LevelImposter.dll and Newtonsoft.Json.dll</li>
	<li>
		Go to your BepInEx's plugins folder
		<ul>
			<li><b>Steam: </b>C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Modded Among Us\BepInEx\plugins</li>
			<li><b>Epic: </b>C:\Program Files\Epic Games\AmongUs\BepInEx\plugins</li>
		</ul>
	</li>
	<li>Put both LevelImposter.dll and Newtonsoft.Json.dll in the folder</li>
	<li>Put the map file in the same folder</li>
	<li>Rename the map file to "map.json"</li>
	<li>Open Among Us</li>
</ol>
<p>
	If LevelImposter succeeded, it should run without issue. If not, feel free to contact us at our discord server: <a href="https://discord.gg/9jJEBQ4qJs">https://discord.gg/9jJEBQ4qJs</a>
</p>